Hull Points: +22.5
Acceleration: −0.3
Turn Acceleration: −0.75 deg/s²
Cost: 8,000
Durability: 2500 / 2500
Effect: Balanced armor + hull with mild maneuver penalties.
Upgrade Axis: Armor and Hull scale.

Strike Hull Plating (L1)
Hull Points: +45 → +108 (upgrades)
Acceleration: −0.2
Turn Acceleration: −1.0 deg/s²
Cost: 8,000
Durability: 6,000 / 6,000
Effect: Baseline hull module for Strike-class ships that increases maximum Hull Points at the expense of slightly reduced linear acceleration and noticeably reduced turn acceleration. Provides a straightforward survivability boost for fragile Strike hulls without altering Armor Value.
Upgrade Axis: Hull Points scale with item level from +45 at L1 up to +108 at L15. Acceleration and turn-acceleration penalties remain fixed at all levels.

