Critical Defense: +1.5 → +3.6 (upgrades)
Hull Points: +140 → +336 (upgrades)
Acceleration: −0.05
Turn Acceleration: −0.1 deg/s²
Cost: 16,000
Durability: 42,000 / 42,000
Effect: Composite heavy-tuned module that simultaneously boosts Armor Value, Critical Defense, and Hull Points for Line-class ships. Provides broad defensive coverage with moderate but manageable penalties to acceleration and turning.
Upgrade Axis: Armor Value scales from +1.4 at L1 to +3.36 at L15; Critical Defense scales from +1.5 at L1 to +3.6 at L15; Hull Points scale from +140 at L1 to +336 at L15. Acceleration and turn-acceleration penalties remain fixed.

Line System Redundancy (L1) – Passive
Hull Recovery: +3.5 /sec → +8.4 /sec (upgrades)
Cost: 10,000
Durability: 42,000 / 42,000
Effect: Passive hull system for Line-class ships that increases natural Hull Point recovery over time, improving sustain without altering Armor, Hull capacity, or movement stats.
Upgrade Axis: Hull Recovery scales from +3.5 HP/sec at L1 up to +8.4 HP/sec at L15. No other attributes are modified.

Line Damage Control (L1) – Active
Hullpoint Restore: +350 → +840 (upgrades)
Reload: 30 s
Power Cost: 250
Cost: 16,000
Durability: 42,000 / 42,000
Effect: Active hull repair system for Line-class ships. When activated, instantly restores a large chunk of Hull Points at the cost of ship Power and a 30-second cooldown. Ideal for weathering heavy alpha strikes or buying time to disengage.
Upgrade Axis: Hullpoint Restore scales from +350 at L1 to +840 at L15. Reload and Power Cost remain fixed at all levels.

